-green-review-paris-justice-olympics-3761953">我们爱绿色评论：巴黎的盛夏以家乡英雄正义、L&#39;Imperatrice 等拉开帷幕</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/fcukers-19-08-2024-3784706">前<em>NME</em>封面明星</a><a href="/artists/Fcukers">Fcukers</a> 、Snow Strippers、DJ Koze、Marcel Dettman、Clara Luciani、Lucky Love、Polo &amp; Pan、Avalon Emerson、 <a href="/artists/Sublime">Sublime</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Gesaffelstein">Gesaffelstein</a> 、Judeline、Laylow、Maureen、Paul Kalkbrenner、Theodora、Tiakola、YSEULT 等Zamdane 也已加入阵容， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-to-headline-frances-we-love-green-2025-with-air-kavinsky-and-more-announced-3814173">加入之前宣布的 Charli 行列XCX、Air、Kavinsky、Parcels、Magdalena Bay、HorsegiirL、Spill Tab 等</a>。</p><p>法国音乐盛典将于 2025 年 6 月 6 日至 8 日重返巴黎文森森林中心，继今年创下超过 110,000 人参加的破纪录活动之后。</p><p> 2025 年音乐节的早鸟票可<a href="https://www.welovegreen.fr/billetterie/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买。周末通行证起价为 159 欧元（132 英镑），工作日单程票起价为 64 欧元（53 英镑）。 </p><figure id="attachment_3823193" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3823193" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3823193" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/We-Love-Green-2025-Second-announce-Poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="我们爱绿色 2025 第二张公布海报。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2493" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/We-Love-Green-2025-Second-announce-Poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/We-Love-Green-2025-Second-announce-Poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x499.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/We-Love-Green-2025-Second-announce-Poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x997.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/We-Love-Green-2025-Second-announce-Poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x868.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/We-Love-Green-2025-Second-announce-Poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1735.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/1